# Example environment variables — copy to .env.local and fill in real values.
#
# NOTE: This project currently requires NO runtime environment variables.
# Site content is fetched at build time from public Google Sheets CSV exports,
# whose URLs are hardcoded in `src/lib/services/config/csvUrls.ts`.
# Deploys are triggered by a Vercel Deploy Hook that lives in Google Apps Script
# (outside this repository), not via an env var here.
#
# Add real variables below as the project grows, e.g.:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SOME_API_KEY=your_value_here
# VERCEL_DEPLOY_HOOK_URL=your_value_here
